steps.name: Given  I go to the 'Google Home' page
And  On the 'Google Home' page, in the 'Search Text' I type: 'Manchester City'
And  On the 'Google Home' page, I click on: 'Search Button'
Then  The first result must contain the text 'Manchester City'
And  On the 'Results' page, I click on: 'The first result'
Then  The title of the page must contain 'Manchester City'
